UNITED STATES FIRE INSURANCE COMPANY, a corporation, et al. v. ALBANY HOTEL, INC. No. 6441. United States Court of Appeals •Tenth Circuit. July 14, 1960. W. Robert Ward, Denver, Colo., for appellants. Charles J. Beise, and George C. Keely, Denver, Colo., for appellee.

Before MURRAH, Chief Judge, and BREITENSTEIN, Circuit Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed on motion of appellants.
